{"tid":588582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九西補選】游蕙禎未動員投票 本土派會否過票成疑","createTime":"2018-03-11T10:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T15:25:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"fbdb35022e4f08c926bd807eabc68f90fe789df1","tid":588582,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520762624_c41d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520762624_c41d.png&h=c4cea8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次的九龍西補選，源於要填補青年新政游蕙禎因宣誓案被褫奪的議席，但作為補選源頭的游蕙禎補選前夕未有呼籲投票，今天亦未見現身任何公開場合助選，她在2016年於九西取得的逾2萬票，料未必全數過票至由民主派初選勝出的姚松炎。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今天曾致電游蕙禎，至今未獲回覆，WhatsApp亦未有回應。翻看游蕙禎的facebook，連日未有談及3.11補選事宜；同樣因為新東議席被褫奪而觸發有關補選的青政梁頌恆，其facebook同樣未見補選消息，近期只談及九巴工潮的問題。<br />\n其實早在民主派就三區直選進行初選之時，青政已經未有參與，梁頌恆更曾澄清，他並非支持於新東參加民主派初選的張秀賢，只是「不反對」本民前的建議人選，又指表態時未定初選機制，質疑初選對推動民主保障自由「有弊無利」。游蕙禎亦曾表明，原則上反對民主派進行初選，她也不會支持任何人選。<br />\n除游蕙禎外，2016年九西補選尚有被歸類本土派的黃毓民，黃與游當年合共得票逾4萬，佔近14.7%。在游、黃均未有動員下，本土派選票流向成關鍵。而當年溫和民主派與劉小麗自決派的得票率約為42.6%，而建制兩大陣營民建聯與經民聯的得票率則為36.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180311/57932683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F57932683&d=n4LuCQ6OSPaO9li2%2F7zAc0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=0af6ff4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F57932683&h=32e6a4df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180311/57932683</a>"},{"pid":"983c091561ca855858b95bd60b074953b5f3921d","tid":588582,"uid":38671,"like":100,"dislike":5,"score":95,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"哇屌真係老馮要投架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cee5851599313fb3ae3954d994d648b4108cf42","tid":588582,"uid":10089,"like":104,"dislike":3,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"動你老母員咩 又唔係有本土派選<br />\n搶撚左人個位仲要人幫返你？"},{"pid":"401f0d6cc7d9f3e4cb558244a206a6cb19d61e49","tid":588582,"uid":80814,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，爛果日報<br />\n咁都有得瀨？"},{"pid":"446f493caef7811afab34663947704c98516aae4","tid":588582,"uid":35221,"like":109,"dislike":3,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人哋贏又屌、人哋畀人DQ又屌、補選唔出嚟選又屌、補選唔動員投票都要屌<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母啦毒果，而家重要屌埋連你班仆街犯民都唔撚當係人嘅本土派唔過票畀你犯民？屌你老母，點解一個畀你哋日屌夜屌嘅人而家要幫你犯民？老撚奉㗎屌你老母？！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f3ce38bcfd043eae1a6d853e494105b79f5f6f19","tid":588582,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"遊B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1e5d689d816ea32786370d9113cf5039521d84","tid":588582,"uid":4783,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"點解要動員？<br />\n游蕙禎又無選，依家老奉要投泛民架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲未計你搵左人地個位黎選，有無問過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續屌票啦白痴毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正視聽，建立時間 (HKT): 0311 18:04，岩岩出的<br />\n真係屌票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97428f46b146968fcbd5f7b10c08d28367e05732","tid":588582,"uid":35070,"like":